FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781453487
OL,3,CBrother of killed student 'aged five
OL,4,Cyears' when he learnt of his death
OL,6,FThe teenager said he was told by a
OL,7,Fteacher that his parents were on their
OL,8,Fway to collect him from school in June
OL,9,F2023, and realised something bad must
OL,10,Fhave happened.
OL,12,F"I was in year 10, first year of
OL,13,FGCSEs, and I'd just come back from
OL,14,Fmessing around with my mates on a
OL,15,Fschool trip," he told The Sunday Times.
OL,17,F"Suddenly there were news crews
OL,18,Foutside our front door. I aged five
OL,19,Fyears just like that."
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@MO]yD@AOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781453487
OL,3,CBrother of killed student 'aged five
OL,4,Cyears' when he learnt of his death
OL,6,FHe told the paper it was a "really
OL,7,Fhard thing to wrap your head around `
OL,8,Fthe idea that someone becomes stuck in
OL,9,Ftime when something like this happens.
OL,11,F"In my head, Barney is three or four
OL,12,Fyears on from the age he was when he
OL,13,Fpassed away, but actually he's frozen
OL,14,Fat 19."
OL,16,FDescribing how the family dynamic has
OL,17,Fchanged since his brother died, he
OL,18,Fsaid he felt "pressure," as "I was
OL,19,Ftrying to keep myself out of trouble,
OL,20,Faway from anything bad, away from
OL,21,Fbeing in danger".
OL,26,@nD@\OUsD@AOUvD@GO]zD@NOUzD@XO]zD@]OU}D@
OL,26,APO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781453487
OL,3,CBrother of killed student 'aged five
OL,4,Cyears' when he learnt of his death
OL,6,F"I kept thinking, 'my parents have
OL,7,Falready lost a child. If something
OL,8,Fhappened to me, it'd be brutal for
OL,9,Fthem'."
OL,11,FHe said he did not want to undertake
OL,12,Ftherapy to start with, as "I didn't
OL,13,Fwant the stigma", but added that
OL,14,Feventually having it has helped him
OL,15,F"massively".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@GO]tD@[OUuD@PO]wD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781453487
OL,3,CBrother of killed student 'aged five
OL,4,Cyears' when he learnt of his death
OL,6,FCalocane was sentenced to an
OL,7,Findefinite hospital order after he
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to manslaughter and
OL,9,Fattempted murder over the killing of
OL,10,FMr Webber, Grace O'Malley-Kumar, 19,
OL,11,Fand school caretaker Ian Coates, 65,
OL,12,Fbefore he tried to murder three
OL,13,Fpedestrians with a van.
OL,15,FMr Webber's mother, Emma Webber, has
OL,16,Fclaimed it was a "miscarriage of
OL,17,Fjustice" that Calocane "got away with
OL,18,Fmurder" after the Crown Prosecution
OL,19,FService accepted his not guilty pleas
OL,20,Fto murder on the grounds of diminished
OL,21,Fresponsibility.
OL,26,@xD@ROUyD@HO]yD@XOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781453487
OL,3,CBrother of killed student 'aged five
OL,4,Cyears' when he learnt of his death
OL,6,FAn inquiry into the attacks recently
OL,7,Ffinished hearing evidence, with the
OL,8,Ffindings due to be published next year.
OL,10,F"I could feel the anger building up"
OL,12,FLast week she called on the Government
OL,13,Fto meet her as she said there must be
OL,14,Fan independent re-examination of
OL,15,FCalocane's prosecution and sentencing.
OL,17,FMr Webber said that after the
OL,18,Fsentencing, he "was not in a good
OL,19,Fstate mentally. I was really upset,
OL,20,Freally angry".
OL,26,@zD@POU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781453487
OL,3,CBrother of killed student 'aged five
OL,4,Cyears' when he learnt of his death
OL,6,F"I could feel the anger slowly
OL,7,Fbuilding up, and that's when I
OL,8,Frealised I had to dial myself in and
OL,9,Ffocus this energy on something that
OL,10,Fcan be positive."
OL,12,FHe said he has now thrown himself into
OL,13,Fthe Barnaby Webber Foundation, a
OL,14,Fcharity set up to support young people
OL,15,Fwho are facing life challenges, and is
OL,16,Ffollowing his family's motto to "be
OL,17,Fmore Barney".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@QO]xD@aOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1781453487
OL,3,CBrother of killed student 'aged five
OL,4,Cyears' when he learnt of his death
OL,6,F"I felt like I needed to step up a
OL,7,Flittle bit and get behind the cause. I
OL,8,Fneeded to fight for what we think is
OL,9,Fright," he added.
OL,11,FMr Webber said watching his parents
OL,12,Fduring the inquiry has given him "a
OL,13,Fhuge sense of pride".
OL,15,F"They're so strong," he added.
OL,17,F"It's incredible that someone can go
OL,18,Ffrom being so devastated and upset in
OL,19,Fprivate to putting on a brave face."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@GO]tD@bOUuD@TO]wD@AOUwD@TO]yD@
OL,26,AAOU{D@dO]
